With this minor release automounter gains the ability to detect optical drives
without present media. It also adds automatic discovery for most available
disk provider. I.e. automatic discovery is no longer limited to USB devices.

- automounter 1.4.2

 * Tested on FreeBSD 8.0-STABLE
 Please run 'man 8 automounter' and 'man 5 automounter.conf' for introductions.
